➜网曝李易峰疑恋上李雨桐闺蜜同游苏梅岛 女方回应：没有的事
http://www.sohu.com/a/299143795_100220830	13950
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为娱乐圈内的知名流量小生，李易峰的恋情一直是广大粉丝们所关注的焦点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190305/dc3a146e1f3e4b2e8bc0d8fe073b6af0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">日前，有网友爆料李易峰疑似恋上一名叫“湾湾”的网红，两人还在2019年元旦同游苏梅岛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190305/f235c61cd1cb4f64bf7270a2db94285a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190305/cd5477c7fe0c48ca822aeda225e42e0d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
